==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Toweling
<hw>Tow"el*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Cloth for towels, especially
such as is woven in long pieces to be cut at will, as distinguished from
that woven in towel lengths with borders, etc.</def> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>towelling</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tower</ent>⟦br⟧
